To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private SimpleMovingAverage _sma;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_sma = SMA(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_sma.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "rollingsum", _sma.RollingSum.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "simplemovingaverage", _sma.Current.Value);
}
